result.adr_address: 14 Shelley St, Central, Hong Kong
result.name: Motorino

reviews.text: The pizza couldn’t meet my high expectations I have for a pizzeria with such a wonderful oven. Of course it’s still better then most other pizzerias, but also much worse than a good pizzeria in Napoli.

This is almost certainly the best pizza in Hong Kong. It's pricey even by Hong Kong standards but the quality is absolutely top notch. I tried both the recommended house red and a white wine. They were both okay, didn't knock me over--those were the cheapest selections though! 

Highly recommend a visit for authentic Neapolitan pizza!

Great tasting pizzas, salads and friendly service staff (particularly Yamoona who looked after our table). They are very generous with their pizza toppings, and allow you to mix up to 2 flavors for a pizza. The pizza dough is chewy and tasty.

My only suggestion for the restaurant is to serve the pizzas on a wooden platter so that it doesn’t sweat underneath.
Love love love their pizza 🍕 and the staff. Friendly well trained professional. Simply a good choice for a pizza night!

Great, casual place to get good pizza at great value in central. Choose a base/flavour, add some toppings if wanted, and enjoy a very filling portion of pizza! Wine and beer options come with, and both indoor and semi-outdoor seating options are available. Overall always had a great time here when visiting, and the staff and the decor definitely add their part to the experience.

result.name: Motorino

reviews.text:
離灣仔捷運站步行約10-15分鐘

披薩餅皮算是薄Q的～
四人點了辣味臘腸跟肉丸披薩～
辣味算小辣，是屬於辣油的辣！

非常好吃！！！！
開胃菜烤玉米的醬汁微辣提味！
好吃！

吃不完還可以外帶，
包裝十分方便！

센트럴미드레벨 에스칼레이터를 올라가다 보면
중간에 위치하고 있습니다. 
직원들이 친절하고 코지한 분위기였어요. 

직원 분이 추천해 주신 메뉴 중
고르곤졸라 피자 선택, 맥주 한잔을 마셨는데
담백하고 맛있었습니다. 
피자 치즈 원재료 맛도 좋았지만
꼭 꿀을 달라고 하셔서 함께 드세요. 
가격대는 HKD 300정도 합니다. 

오후 5시 경에는 붐비지 않고 좋았습니다.

Highly recommend a visit for authentic Neapolitan pizza!

Great tasting pizzas, salads and friendly service staff (particularly Yamoona who looked after our table). They are very generous with their pizza toppings, and allow you to mix up to 2 flavors for a pizza. The pizza dough is chewy and tasty.

My only suggestion for the restaurant is to serve the pizzas on a wooden platter so that it doesn’t sweat underneath.
